Content management software - or more commonly, content management systems - are types of software that allow someone who doesn't know very much about websites to still do some things on the website to change the website - to maintain the website.
We sometimes call these CMS - content management systems.
To be installed, "installed," means to have a program put on your computer or put on your website.
